OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784931509
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway announce plans
OL,4,Cduring strike action
OL,6,FEast Midlands Railway trains will be
OL,7,Faffected by strike action from 1st
OL,8,FAugust.
OL,10,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,11,FTransport union (RMT) have notified
OL,12,Fthe operator that alongside strike
OL,13,Faction on Saturday 1, 8, and 15
OL,14,FAugust, they will be taking action
OL,15,Fshort of a strike during the week.
OL,17,FThey are striking over "growing safety
OL,18,Fconcerns that the company has failed
OL,19,Fto address."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784931509
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway announce plans
OL,4,Cduring strike action
OL,6,FEast Midlands Railway have denied the
OL,7,Fsafety concerns.
OL,9,FThe train operator advised people to
OL,10,Fundertake only essential travel, and
OL,11,Fsaid services could be cancelled or
OL,12,Faltered at short notice.
OL,14,FThey added that no rail replacement
OL,15,Fbuses will be available.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784931509
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway announce plans
OL,4,Cduring strike action
OL,6,FWhen announcing the strike, RMT said
OL,7,Fin a statement: "RMT has been in
OL,8,Fdispute with EMR since April following
OL,9,Fthe roll out of the 810 fleet which
OL,10,Fhas been operating with a significant
OL,11,Fnumber of faults.
OL,13,F"Yet EMR has been sending trains into
OL,14,Fservice that are likely to fail and
OL,15,Frequire a full reset, which leaves the
OL,16,Ftrain with no active safety systems
OL,17,Fincluding loss of communication
OL,18,Fbetween train drivers, dispatchers,
OL,19,Fand trackside which has occurred at
OL,20,Fleast three times in the last week
OL,21,Falone."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784931509
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway announce plans
OL,4,Cduring strike action
OL,6,FPhilippa Cresswell, Customer
OL,7,FExperience Director at East Midlands
OL,8,FRailway, said: "We're sorry to
OL,9,Fcustomers whose journeys will be
OL,10,Faffected by this industrial action.
OL,12,F"We know the disruption this will
OL,13,Fcause and are advising customers to
OL,14,Fonly travel if their journey is
OL,15,Fessential on Saturday 1, 8 and 15
OL,16,FAugust, as we will be operating a
OL,17,Fsignificantly reduced timetable
OL,18,Fbetween 07:00 and 19:00.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784931509
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway announce plans
OL,4,Cduring strike action
OL,6,F"EMR continues to engage in
OL,7,Fconstructive discussions with the RMT
OL,8,Fin the hope of resolving this dispute
OL,9,Fas quickly as possible.
OL,11,F"The dispute relates to concerns
OL,12,Fraised about the introduction of our
OL,13,Fnew Class 810 Aurora fleet. Any
OL,14,Fsuggestion that the trains do not meet
OL,15,Fthe required safety standards is
OL,16,Fincorrect.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784931509
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway announce plans
OL,4,Cduring strike action
OL,6,F"The Class 810 fleet entered passenger
OL,7,Fservice only after successfully
OL,8,Fcompleting all required testing and
OL,9,Fmeeting the rigorous safety standards
OL,10,Frequired by the independent regulator."
OL,12,FEast Midlands Railway have said
OL,13,Fregional services are unaffected by
OL,14,Fthe strike and will operate as normal.
OL,16,FTrains between Nottingham and London
OL,17,Fwill run only once per hour, between
OL,18,F7am and 7pm.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
