FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784931509
OL,3,CEast Midlands Railway announce plans
OL,4,Cduring strike action
OL,6,FThe West Midlands Railway network is
OL,7,Falso affected by a separate strike
OL,8,Faction and will be operating a
OL,9,Fsignificantly reduced service on 31
OL,10,FJuly and 1 August.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/7
